{"type":"session_message","session_id":"ses_288fb41ffffeUSq06sFWgWzUUO","role":"assistant","message_id":"msg_d7704d085001T2Ln907H0JpGub","parts":[{"id":"prt_d7704d881001TESYk3MF3HbDNV","messageID":"msg_d7704d085001T2Ln907H0JpGub","sessionID":"ses_288fb41ffffeUSq06sFWgWzUUO","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_cb54e88774ca46e78dd45dfe","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/workspace/README.rst"},"output":"<path>/workspace/README.rst</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>1: .. image:: https://jazzband.co/static/img/badge.svg\n2:    :target: https://jazzband.co/\n3:    :alt: Jazzband\n4: \n5: .. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/wagtailmenus.svg\n6:    :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/wagtailmenus\n7:    :alt: PyPI Download\n8: \n9: .. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/wagtailmenus.svg\n10:     :alt: PyPi Version\n11:     :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/wagtailmenus\n12: \n13: .. image:: https://github.com/jazzband/wagtailmenus/actions/workflows/test.yml/badge.svg\n14:     :alt: Build Status\n15:     :target: https://github.com/jazzband/wagtailmenus/actions/workflows/test.yml\n16: \n17: .. image:: https://codecov.io/gh/jazzband/wagtailmenus/branch/master/graph/badge.svg\n18:     :alt: Code coverage\n19:     :target: https://codecov.io/gh/jazzband/wagtailmenus\n20: \n21: .. image:: https://readthedocs.org/projects/wagtailmenus/badge/?version=latest\n22:     :alt: Documentation Status\n23:     :target: http://wagtailmenus.readthedocs.io/en/latest/\n24: \n25: \n26: ============\n27: wagtailmenus\n28: ============\n29: \n30: wagtailmenus is an extension for Torchbox's `Wagtail CMS <https://github.com/torchbox/wagtail>`_ to help you manage and render multi-level navigation and simple flat menus in a consistent, flexible way.\n31: \n32: The current version is tested for compatibility with the following:\n33: \n34: - Wagtail versions >= 6.3\n35: - Django versions 4.2, 5.1 and >= 5.2\n36: - Python versions 3.9 to 3.13\n37: \n38: .. image:: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jazzband/wagtailmenus/master/docs/source/_static/images/repeating-item.png\n39: \n40: New to wagtailmenus?\n41: ====================\n42: \n43: Start by reading our `Overview and key concepts <http://wagtailmenus.readthedocs.io/en/stable/overview.html>`_ page.\n44: It will give you a better understand of how the app works, and help you decide whether it is a good fit for your project.\n45: \n46: \n47: How do I use it?\n48: ================\n49: \n50: For everything you need to get up and running with wagtailmenus, `view the official documentation <http://wagtailmenus.readthedocs.io/>`_.\n51: \n52: \n53: Contributing\n54: ============\n55: \n56: Instructions on how to contribute can be found `here <https://wagtailmenus.readthedocs.io/en/stable/contributing/index.html>`_.\n57: \n58: As we are members of a `JazzBand project <https://jazzband.co/projects>`_, `wagtailmenus` contributors should adhere to the `Contributor Code of Conduct <https://jazzband.co/about/conduct>`_.\n\n(End of file - total 58 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":".. image:: https://jazzband.co/static/img/badge.svg\n   :target: https://jazzband.co/\n   :alt: Jazzband\n\n.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/wagtailmenus.svg\n   :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/wagtailmenus\n   :alt: PyPI Download\n\n.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/wagtailmenus.svg\n    :alt: PyPi Version\n    :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/wagtailmenus\n\n.. image:: https://github.com/jazzband/wagtailmenus/actions/workflows/test.yml/badge.svg\n    :alt: Build Status\n    :target: https://github.com/jazzband/wagtailmenus/actions/workflows/test.yml\n\n.. image:: https://codecov.io/gh/jazzband/wagtailmenus/branch/master/graph/badge.svg\n    :alt: Code coverage\n    :target: https://codecov.io/gh/jazzband/wagtailmenus\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"README.rst","time":{"start":1775818299929,"end":1775818299942}}}]}
